miki_module_admin_prune_no_arg:
Clean up your messages in just a second!

`>prune <amount>` - Prunes previous messages by a specific amount.
`>prune <amount> [mention] ` - Prunes previous messages of a specific user by an amount. 
`>prune <amount> [phrase]` - Prunes previous messages that contain a certain phrase by an amount. The phrase must be in quotes. (Ex. `>prune 5 "sad"`)
`>prune <amount> [mention] [phrase]` - Prunes previous messages of a specific user that contain a certain phrase by an amount.
